---
import SiteLayout from "../components/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="大规模云端建图"
  description="展示吉光智界大规模云端建图能力，覆盖 bag 上传、云端处理、点云地图、关键帧和地图数据包输出。"
  currentPath="/cloud-mapping"
>
  <header class="page-hero mapping-hero">
    <img
      src="/assets/hero-l4-autonomy.png"
      alt="大规模云端建图"
      class="hero-media"
      data-parallax
    />
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-grid"></div>
    <div class="page-hero-shell">
      <div class="page-hero-copy reveal" data-reveal>
        <p class="page-kicker">PAGE 08 · CLOUD MAPPING</p>
        <h1 class="page-title">大规模云端建图</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">
          上传现场采集的 bag 文件，在云端完成点云地图生成、关键帧提取和首帧 GPS 标定。公开页面展示建图流程；上传、处理和下载进入私有工作台后按权限开放。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="page-main grid-bg">
    <section class="page-section">
      <div class="glass-card section-card reveal" data-reveal>
        <p class="section-kicker">建图流程</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">从采集 bag 到可用于定位的地图数据包</h2>
        <div class="page-grid-three">
          <article class="page-card">
            <h3>上传 bag</h3>
            <p>接收现场激光雷达采集数据，识别传感器、坐标系和时间戳信息。</p>
          </article>
          <article class="page-card">
            <h3>云端处理</h3>
            <p>调用云端建图流程完成点云配准、地图优化和关键帧提取。</p>
          </article>
          <article class="page-card">
            <h3>地图输出</h3>
            <p>输出点云地图、关键帧数据和首帧 GPS 信息，供自动驾驶定位链路使用。</p>
          </article>
        </div>
        <div class="chip-list">
          <a class="chip-item" href="/app/cloud-mapping">进入云端建图工作台</a>
          <span class="chip-item">需要建图权限</span>
          <span class="chip-item">服务端先鉴权</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</SiteLayout>
